            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Blackwind, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "a top-down sci-fi platformer brawler, you play as James as you survive hordes of aliens inside of the titular combat mech. Heavily armed and assisted by Blackwind’s onboard AI, James searches for his lost father while caught in the middle of the tense struggle between the military and the marauding aliens. ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
